  "title": "Operation Executive",
  "description": "<p>Duties & Responsibilities</p><ul><li>inventory data entry and documentation.</li><li>work closely with production team to manage and analyse inventory balance.</li><li>improve inventory processes.</li><li>produce inventory report for management’s review.</li><li>and any other duties assigned from time to time.</li></ul><p>Job Requirements</p><ul><li>Diploma or Bachelor’s degree holders. </li><li>Proficient in Microsoft Excel.</li><li>Excellent numeric skills with exceptional attention to details.</li><li>Good working attitude, meticulous & independent.</li><li>Workplace is located in Tuas, and company transport is provided from Jurong East MRT.</li></ul>",
